[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0527","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0527.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0315","title":"Sun Solaris fdformat 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 fdformat 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。fdformat 是格式化软盘的工具，设置了 setuid root 权限。本地用户可通过向该命令传递超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.4 及更早版本，攻击者需要拥有本地 shell 访问权限，成功利用后可获得完全 root 控制权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0315"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.140","remediation":"建议升级到 Solaris 2.6 及以上版本，或安装 Sun 官方补丁 105401-01。临时缓解措施可移除 fdformat 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /bin/fdformat。限制本地用户对 fdformat 的访问权限亦可降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/138","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/328"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0527.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0486","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0486.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0292","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Winpopup 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 Winpopup（信使服务）在处理用户名字段时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送包含超长用户名的弹出消息触发该漏洞，导致目标系统耗尽系统资源或信使服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击复杂度较低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。Microsoft 官方未发布针对此漏洞的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0292"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.240","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 以修复 Winpopup 消息处理中的缓冲区问题。如系统已不受支持，建议立即升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本，或在防火墙和本地安全策略中禁用 Messenger 服务（net stop messenger）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0292","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0292","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0292.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5hp9-m282-4fm5/GHSA-5hp9-m282-4fm5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d5e467d6-9db2-4f83-aa80-400388f5bd0e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0486.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0466","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0466.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0280","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"微软 Internet Explorer 浏览器存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过构造特制的 .lnk 快捷方式文件或 .url 链接文件，诱使用户点击后在当前用户上下文环境中执行任意命令。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需身份认证，影响使用 Internet Explorer 的 Windows 系统。由于 IE 对 .lnk 和 .url 文件的处理缺乏充分校验，导致攻击者可在用户浏览网页时触发恶意操作。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0280"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.833","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 及以上版本，或安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-013 对应补丁。该漏洞已在新版 IE 中修复，建议立即停止使用旧版 IE，改用 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。如因兼容性必须使用，可在安全设置中将「Internet 区域」和「受限站点区域」的安全级别设为「高」，并禁用「下载未签名的 ActiveX 控件」。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0280","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0280","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0280.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hjxm-3j2g-hph3/GHSA-hjxm-3j2g-hph3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/CrackerCat/simpread/blob/1ec36a5827997f39a7a815e20121b12f8d781497/md/Chrome%20Browser%20Exploitation,%20Part%201:%20Introduction%20to%20V8%20and%20JavaScript%20Internals%20-%20Jack%20Hacks.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0466.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0495","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0495.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0299","title":"FreeBSD lpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 的 lpd（行式打印机守护进程）在处理超长 DNS 主机名时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的打印服务发送特制的主机名数据触发该溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0299"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.117","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 至已修复该漏洞的版本（4.0 及以上）。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 lpd 行并重启 inetd 以禁用打印机守护进程；若需继续使用 lpd，在 /etc/hosts.lpd 和白名单中限制允许访问的客户端 IP，并在防火墙层面阻止外部对 TCP 515 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6093","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0299","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0299.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/lpd_freebsd_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83077/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0495.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0892","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0892.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0612","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 Finger 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统默认安装的 finger 服务存在信息泄露漏洞。finger 协议设计上未对请求来源进行任何认证或限制，允许网络上的任何攻击者向目标主机的 finger 服务（默认端口 79）发送查询请求，从而获取系统上有效的用户名列表及其他用户账户信息。攻击者可利用收集到的有效用户名进行后续的口令猜测、暴力破解或社会工程学攻击，进一步威胁系统安全。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 等版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0612"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.177","remediation":"停止 Finger 服务（运行 services.msc，找到 \"Finger Service\" 设置为禁用），并在防火墙层面屏蔽 TCP 端口 79 以阻止外部访问。如需使用 finger 功能，应升级到不再内置该服务的 Windows XP 或更高版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0612","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0612.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0612","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/finger/CVE-1999-0612.nopatch","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/324.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0612.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8873-vgfq-r935/GHSA-8873-vgfq-r935.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/finger.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0892.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0530","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0530.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0318","title":"HP-UX XMCD 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"xmcd 2.0p12 在处理环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向受影响程序传递特制的环境变量参数触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区边界溢出并覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取目标系统的额外访问权限或提升至更高权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统上运行的 xmcd 2.0p12 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级到不受影响的版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0318"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.507","remediation":"升级 xmcd 至 2.1 及以上版本（该版本已修复缓冲区溢出问题）。如无法升级，可移除 xmcd 二进制文件的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xmcd`；若业务不需要 CD 播放功能，建议直接卸载 xmcd 软件包以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0318"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0530.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0241","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0241.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0106","title":"多种厂商 Finger 服务手指炸弹漏洞","description":"Finger 服务存在重定向功能滥用漏洞，远程攻击者可利用多个支持 Finger 协议的主机构建重定向链（finger bomb），迫使目标系统反复进行网络连接，造成流量放大或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响早期运行 Finger 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。建议禁用 Finger 服务或通过防火墙限制入站访问。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0106"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.040","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务（如 in.fingerd），在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释掉 finger 行并重启服务。在防火墙上阻止外部对 TCP 端口 79 的访问。如确需使用，通过 tcp_wrappers（/etc/hosts.deny）限制仅允许可信来源 IP。建议升级到支持 finger 访问控制的实现或直接停用该协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0106"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0241.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0336","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0336.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0165","title":"Linux Linux 内核 NFS 缓存中毒漏洞","description":"NFS（网络文件系统）缓存投毒漏洞，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标系统上的 NFS 服务发送特制的 RPC 请求来污染客户端缓存，从而将文件操作重定向至恶意服务器，导致敏感信息泄露、文件篡改乃至任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 SunOS、Solaris 及早期 Linux 发行版中运行的 NFS 服务，CVSS v2 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全补丁加以修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0165"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-01","updated":"1997-03-01","remediation":"在 /etc/exports 中使用完全限定域名（FQDN）替代非限定主机名，避免网组（netgroup）配置歧义。同时建议在服务端升级对应厂商补丁（如 Sun、Red Hat、SUSE 等当时的 NFS 安全更新），并在边界防火墙限制外部对 NFS 端口（2049/TCP、2049/UDP）的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0336.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0238","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0238.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0105","title":"多款Unix系统 finger 递归查询信息泄露漏洞","description":"finger 服务在处理包含连续 @ 符号的递归查询请求时存在设计缺陷。远程攻击者可通过向目标主机的 finger 服务（默认端口 79）发送精心构造的包含多个 @ 符号的长字符串，触发递归查询机制，导致服务资源被过度消耗从而引发拒绝服务，同时也可被用于跨网络用户信息枚举，泄露系统用户名等敏感信息。该漏洞影响大量运行 finger 服务的 UNIX/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0105"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1997-03-01","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.913","remediation":"建议直接禁用 finger 服务（在 inetd 配置中注释 finger 行并重启 inetd 服务），或在网络防火墙层面阻止 TCP 79 端口的入站与出站流量。若业务必须使用，应升级至支持限制递归查询的 fingerd 实现，或限制可查询的用户列表。现代生产环境建议彻底移除 finger 协议及相关软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0105","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0105"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0238.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0104","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0041","title":"多款Unix系统libc NLS组件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NLS（自然语言服务）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向受影响系统发送特制的 NLS 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致系统崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 UNICOS 9、MAX 1.3、AIX 4.2、IRIX 6、RedHat 4、Slackware 3、libc 5.2.18 及 mk 1.5 等多个 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。由于涉及系统核心库组件，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0041"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.153","remediation":"对于 Red Hat Linux 4/Slackware 3 等 Linux 系统，应升级至现代发行版并确保 glibc 版本高于 2.0（含 NLS 缓冲区溢出修复）；IBM AIX 4.2 用户请安装 APAR IX70456 补丁或升级至 AIX 5.3 及以上版本；SGI IRIX 6 用户应安装补丁 3369 或升级至 IRIX 6.5.4+。如无法升级，可移除 nls 可执行文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/nls），并限制仅受信用户可执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0041","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19551","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0041","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0041.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pqw7-9pjx-g2x6/GHSA-pqw7-9pjx-g2x6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0250","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0250.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0109","title":"Sun Solaris ffbconfig 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 的 ffbconfig 图形配置工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 ffbconfig 程序传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖进程内存空间，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需要拥有本地系统账号才能利用此漏洞实施提权攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0109"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.407","remediation":"立即应用 Sun Security Bulletin #140 提供的补丁程序，或直接升级到 Solaris 7 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/sbin/ffbconfig 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/ffbconfig），限制本地非授权用户执行该命令，防止普通用户利用缓冲区溢出提权至 root。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19159","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0109","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0109.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7xv-wfqv-x2wf/GHSA-m7xv-wfqv-x2wf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0250.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0414","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0414.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0228","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RPC Locator 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 RPC Locator 服务（rpcss.exe）存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求，导致 RPC 定位服务进程崩溃或停止响应，影响系统正常功能。该漏洞无需身份认证即可触发，攻击复杂度低，危害等级中等。Microsoft 官方已发布安全更新解决此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0228"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.410","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对此漏洞发布的热修复补丁 KB Q162567，该补丁解决了 rpcss.exe 在处理特定 RPC 请求时的拒绝服务问题。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已于 2004 年终止支持且不再接收安全更新，建议升级至仍在支持周期内的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：在不需要 RPC Locator 服务的环境中，通过 services.msc 将 Remote Procedure Call (RPC) Locator 服务启动类型设为\"禁用\"，或在防火墙上限制对该服务端口 (TCP 135) 的不必要访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ162567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0228","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0228.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7hpc-4h5x-v8cw/GHSA-7hpc-4h5x-v8cw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0414.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0116","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0116.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0046","title":"多款Unix系统 rlogin TERM环境变量缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"rlogin 程序在处理 TERM 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可向该环境变量传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS、DG/UX、Debian、Digital UNIX、FreeBSD、HP-UX、IBM AIX、NetBSD、NeXTstep、SGI IRIX、SunOS 等多种 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0046"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.963","remediation":"针对各受影响系统版本，建议立即升级至修复版本（如 FreeBSD 2.2 及以上、HP-UX 11.00 及以上、IBM AIX 4.2 及以上）；如无法升级，可移除 rlogin 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/rlogin）或禁用 rlogin 服务（注释 inetd.conf 中 login 行并重启 inetd），改用 SSH 替代 rlogin 进行远程登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0046","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19203","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0046","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/622953dc0146a9a48737afdaeb97da06c1b9895d/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0116.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0116.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0116.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0494","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0494.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0298","title":"SunOS ypbind 路径遍历文件覆盖漏洞","description":"SunOS 与 Linux Slackware 系统中 ypbind 服务在启用 -ypset 或 -ypsetme 选项时存在路径遍历漏洞。远程或本地攻击者可通过构造包含 ..（点点）的特殊请求，绕过目录限制覆盖系统任意文件，导致权限提升或服务异常。该漏洞影响运行 ypbind 且开启上述选项的 SunOS 及 Slackware 系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0298"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.990","remediation":"禁止使用 -ypset 和 -ypsetme 参数启动 ypbind，仅允许通过 ypserv 配置文件（/var/yp/securenets）确定的受信 NIS 服务器绑定。在防火墙层面限制 UDP 端口 111 和 32770-32800 的外部访问，或禁用 NIS 改用 LDAP 认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/06_ypbindsetme_adv.asp","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-0298.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0298","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0298.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1441/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000146.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0494.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0607","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0607.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0369","title":"Sun Solaris OpenWindows sdtcm_convert 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中 OpenWindows 环境的 sdtcm_convert 日历转换工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向该程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 及更早版本，需要本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0369"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.910","remediation":"立即应用 Sun 安全公告 #183 提供的补丁，升级 sdtcm_convert 至修复版本。如无法打补丁，执行 `chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/sdtcm_convert` 移除 setuid 位以消除本地提权风险，或卸载 OpenWindows 组件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/183","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19128","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0369.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0369","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0369.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0369.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8rf-j665-q782/GHSA-q8rf-j665-q782.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e6c9064b-c174-46c8-964b-e6dfac38cd65.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/19